Check-list for silpo.ua

Header	
	Redirecting to the main page by clicking on the logo
	Open/close the burger menu
	Verify the links in the burger menu redirect to the correct page
	Switch between product categories at "Всі товари"
	Verify clicking on a product category redirects to the correct category page
	Verify the cart icon is displayed
	Verify the cart icon displays the correct items amount 
	Verify the cart icon displays the correct total price
	Verify the login 
	
Search	
  Search with product name
	Search with category name
	
Location	
  Choose the delivery address by searching 
	Choose the delivery address on the map
	Choose the city for pick-up from the menu
	Choose the store for pick-up from the menu
	Choose the store for pick-up on the map
	
Main content	
  Verify the horizontal scroll list has 20 products 
	Verify clicking on a product card redirects to the correct product page
	Verify adding a product from the main page adds it to the cart
	Verify that banners with discounts are displayed 
	Verify that banners with discounts are sliding
	Verify that clicking the banner with a discount redirects to the correct page
	
Footer	
  Verify that clicking on social media links redirects to the correct pages
	Verify downloading the mobile app by link
	Check the footer links redirect to the correct pages
	Verify scroll to top button redirect to the top of the page
